{"tid":1321733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遍地開花 倫敦街頭驚現香蕉糖","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T18:33:22.000Z","uid":130534,"like":772,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"99c126345cb3bfc10f63b04dff63bb0e7b304fe9","tid":1321733,"uid":130534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJqQxHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJqQxHg.png&h=e20627ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3B2vxHj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3B2vxHj.png&h=0d3f1162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqnvxHm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqnvxHm.png&h=24efbd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQi6Qt3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQi6Qt3.png&h=4198c71b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ef82be8fa5bb053ad3beddcfc3c6a4cb83bb32","tid":1321733,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d09470c2f1dc574b5b29e3737bd48051edd3848","tid":1321733,"uid":275490,"like":467,"dislike":1,"score":466,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"英文都唔轉人地點睇啊"},{"pid":"f66f6809168fba48ce0aaa55003648aef2428752","tid":1321733,"uid":6848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:01:10.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0c8cc62d0de9ca5e688451f0ec604b83a3abbb","tid":1321733,"uid":95102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721聲明</span></div><br />\n<br />\n我們一眾香港人謹此聲明，我們在6月9日及6月16日已經以和平、理性、非暴力的方式，進行和平遊行表達過我們的訴求但政府屢次漠視民意、又以前線警員作為擋箭牌，故此我們於2019年7月21日的一切行動都是以五大訴求為目的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求包括：<br />\n<br />\n1.要求政府確實地使用「撤回」的字眼<br />\n撤回《2019年逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例（修訂）條例草案》（即《逃犯條例》）<br />\n<br />\n2.撤回612暴動定性，警方於6月12日晚上發出的反對集會通知書，其中列明警方將當日「集會定性為暴動」故此我們要求政府撤回6月12日遊行示威的暴動定性。<br />\n<br />\n3.不檢控、釋放及撤回所有抗爭者控罪，連日以來的遊行示威中有多名示威者被警方拘捕，我們要求警方釋放「由6月9日至政府承諾此項訴求當日」的所有示威者，並且永不追究，包括但不限於以下兩項：<br />\n一、不以任何形式、任何罪名拘捕、控告任何示威者<br />\n二、確保所有示威者不被任何國家機構侵害人身自由以及財產利益<br />\n<br />\n4.追究警隊濫權，於連日以來的遊行示威中，警方多次未有展示委任證及警員編號包括 ：快速應變小隊（速龍小隊）， 雖然保安局局長李家超指該小隊制服未有足夠位置展示警員編號，但在2016年旺角警民衝突中其肩章仍縫有警員編號。<br />\n另外警方多次以過分武力驅趕示威者，包括在示威者後退時使用警棍、胡椒噴劑、 催淚彈等驅逐正在和平退去的示威者，又以警棍、胡椒噴劑襲擊穿上反光衣及已表明身份的記者，我們強烈譴責這些濫權的行為並且要求政府成立獨立調查委員會，追究濫用武力警員。<br />\n<br />\n5.落實雙普選，政府在連日以來的遊行示威多次漠視民意，甚至有與香港市民作對之嫌，所以問題根本在於香港政府本身，我們要求政府以行政命令解散立法會、立即實行香港人一人一票普選立法會議員及行政長官。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於政府現時一直拒絕回應示威者訴求， 令到事態惡化，警民關係繃緊， 加劇社會撕裂，我們促請政府正面回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n在政府達到五大訴求前我們不會罷休， 並且會以一切方法迫使政府達到我們的訴求，但只要政府能夠達到我們的訴求，一眾示威者可以回復正常生活，香港人民就可以回復安定的生活，社會撕裂就會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我們一眾香港人在此促請香港政府正面回應五大訴求。</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"745aca3ca2dd0a1379c5fc349e5dacf31672c5b4","tid":1321733,"uid":74876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f56cd9e4add603245feda92f8333652a489fe44","tid":1321733,"uid":105924,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"防暴警會唔會黎埋英國撕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a953e7c88581668f59e1e659bfb83be7da8f24f9","tid":1321733,"uid":160528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b7bd873a57cecc52a830c947d6e180f4423464","tid":1321733,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f2a6f563cef788484a2bc299c2b01c830f2ad8","tid":1321733,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bc936c4b7163a3fe71fb64f734764ffb4231df","tid":1321733,"uid":200687,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"遠近馳名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港終於有手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3335e081d071f52ec2e3cb144820bc5d96217392","tid":1321733,"uid":130534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b741f65797a6c8735a0dc925751cbff7bd09e","tid":1321733,"uid":217080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d1da3c05437d1d5c93b167e3ed78438b066094","tid":1321733,"uid":894,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy